snippet.textDisplay: Madison is an entitled selfish brat. There are so many red flags with her. Peter is just defending her because he already looked like a fool with Hannah Ann so if he were to go back on his word and say he no longer has feelings for Madison he would get so much hate. I'm glad the mom and the family stood their ground. Anyone rooting for Madison is just as selfish, entitled, and a toxic feminist as she is.
